title: HealthLink - AI Telemedicine Platform
description: AI-powered telemedicine platform with Patient and doctor dashboards
Video/Audio calls, Chat, Call transcription & LLM-powered video calls
Secure appointment scheduling, E-prescriptions & Integrated payment solutions
Deployed on fly.io & github pages using Docker with CI/CD

title: Ecommerce - ETL Pipeline, Web Scraper
description: ETL pipeline on Google Cloud with container orchestration for high availability & scalability
Google Firestore for scalable, and real-time data storage
Algolia for indexing and search functionality, enabling fast search results within the mobile app
Reliable web scraper to continuously extract up-to-date product data.
